"Afternoon tea" /><meta itemprop="recipeCategory" content="Dessert" /><meta itemprop="recipeCategory" content="Treat" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Shortbread recipe" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Mother&#039;s day recipe" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Mother&#039;s day" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="mother&#039;s day biscuits" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Edible flowers" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Shortbread" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="sugared flower" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Easter" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="More effort" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Mother&#039;s Day" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Cakes and Bakes" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Celebration" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Weekend" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Spring" /></div></div><div class="recipe-header__description" itemprop="description"><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden method__content"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>These delicate shortbreads make a perfect gift. Given a floral hint&nbsp;with rosewater, you could also use&nbsp;orange blossom extract or dried lavender</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="recipe-header__bottom"><div class="recipe-header__share service-links__container"><div class="service-links"><div class="service-label">Share:</div><ul class="service-links-primary"><li class="service-links-facebook first"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/sugared-flower-shortbreads&amp;t=Sugared%20flower%20shortbreads" title="Share on Facebook" class="service-links-facebook service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Facebook"><i class="font-icon font-icon-facebook-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Facebook</span></a></li><li class="service-links-pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/bookmarklet?media=https%3A//www.b