4/open-flower-dumplings"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--17469_12.jpg?itok=HnhyF7gP" width="468" height="382" alt="Open flower dumplings" title="Open flower dumplings" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Recipe</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Open flower dumplings</h3><div class="push-item__ratings"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-average-text"><div class="fivestar-static-form-item"><div class="form-item form-type-item"><div class="field-main"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">3.75</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="off"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="description"><p class="fivestar-summary fivestar-summary-">(2 <span class="rating-text"> ratings</span>)</p></div></div></div></div></div> </a></article><article id="node-100752" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-recipe node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/recipes/2369637/stuffed-courgette-flowers"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--1047536_11.jpg?itok=hGvKQ0m3" width="468" height="382" alt="Stuffed courgette flowers" title="Stuffed courgette flowers" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Recipe</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Stuffed courgette flowers</h3><div class="push-item__ratings"><div class="clearfix fi